Dixy Group to Spend $23 Million on Upgrade of Its Retail Network

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-05-30T17:58:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-30/dixy-group-to-spend-23-million-on-upgrade-of-its-retail-network.html
OAO Dixy Group, a Russian supermarket
chain, plans to spend 664 million rubles ($23 million) on
changing the format of its retail network, President Ilya
Yakubson said in a video conference from  London .  The company wants to target consumers of below-average
wealth in addition to average-wealth customers, Yakubson said
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow at 
